snippet.title: Amber Heard, Patrick Wilson & James Wan talk Aquaman
snippet.description:
Amber Heard, Patrick Wilson and Director James Wan are interviewed for their movie Aquaman, the latest in the DC / Justice League franchise.

Patrick Wilson argues that his character looks more like Legolas than Eminem, working with James Wan again.

Amber Heard talks about the joy of not being a reactionary damsel in distress, and how the hyper-sexualisation of women does not accurately define most women.

James Wan talks about walking the fine line between the colourful comic book and the serious environmental and family-themed  elements at play. 

Arthur Curry learns that he is the heir to the underwater kingdom of Atlantis, and must step forward to lead his people and be a hero to the world.
